===Adjective===
'''оба''' (óba) {{m}} & {{n}}, [[обе]] (óbe) {{f}}

# [[both]]
#:*''Usage note: '''''оба''''' in the [[nominative case|nominative]] or [[accusative case]] governs the [[genitive case|genitive]] [[singular]] of the noun; '''''обе''''' in the [[nominative case|nominative]] or [[accusative case]] governs the [[nominative case|nominative]] [[plural]]. An intervening adjective will be in the [[nominative case|nominative]] [[plural]]. In the other cases, '''''оба'''/'''обе''''' and any intervening adjective must all agree with the case of the noun.''
#:*{{RUchar|о́ба [[белый|бе́лые]] [[стол|стола́]]}} — ''both new tables''
#:*{{RUchar|о́ба [[новый|но́вые]] [[окно|о́кна]]}} — ''both white windows''
#:*{{RUchar|о́бе [[хороший|хоро́шие]] [[книга|кни́ги]]}} — ''both good books''
*But:
#:*{{RUchar|с обо́ими [[русский|ру́сскими]] [[солдат|солда́тами]]}} — ''with both Russian soldiers''
#:*{{RUchar|об обе́их [[английский|англи́йских]] [[книга|кни́гах]]}} — ''about both English books''

